summary.description:
Today, cooler for the outside temperature (down 3.4°C), feels like temperature (down 3.0°C), and inside temperature (down 1.6°C) and drier conditions in rainfall (down 0.3 mm).

Compared to today, yesterday also had noticeable differences in cloud levels (up 154 m).

The past week and month had observable variation in feels like temperature (up 7.6°C), dew point temperature (up 6.2°C), outside temperature (up 6.7°C), and cloud levels (up 514 m) when compared to today.
